# Local Dev Rules

## Stack
- Local uses:
  - Docker Postgres
  - Local Uvicorn backend
  - Local portals (Vite)
  - Local JWT signer or Auth0 dev tenant

## Commands
- `make local-up` — DB + hub-api + vendor-mock
- `make local-down`
- `make local-sync-db` (alembic upgrade + seed)
- `make install-ui` — npm install for apps + packages
- `make dev-admin` — Admin portal (apps/web-cip, port 5173)
- `make dev-partners` — Vendor portal (apps/web-partners, port 5174)
- `make build-ui` — Build both portals

## Invariants
- Local behavior must match prod semantics:
  - JWT auth
  - Same execute pipeline
